58000.0,"float_shares":1364207.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.44313,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":0.519,"fifty_two_week_high":1266.0,"fifty_two_week_low":646.1,"fifty_day_average":756.666,"two_hundred_day_avg":875.10876,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":1288.75,"all_time_low":646.1,"long_business_summary":"Lakshmi Electrical Control Systems Limited manufactures and sells control panels and engineering plastic components in India and internationally. It operates in three segments: Electricals, Plastics, and Wind Power Generation. The company offers control panels, including power control and motor control centres, textile machinery panels, MCC and PCC fixed and draw out, drive panels, solar inverter panels, control and relay panels, DCS and automation panels, machine tool panels and cabinets, APFC and harmonic control panels, compressor and wind turbine control panels, PLC Cum VFD panels, solar pump controllers, lighting distribution boards, enclosures, and cable harnesses, as well as contract manufacturing services for OEMs; and engineering plastic components, such as machinery, textile, electrical, and switchgear parts, as well as insert mouldings, automotive components, consumer electronic parts, healthcare components, and industrial application products. It also provides commercial tool room products, including thermoplastic injection and hot runner moulds, over and insert mouldings, two and three plate moulds, connector and thermoset injection moulds, high cavitation and medical moulds, and die casting dies; smart energy meters; and electric vehicle chargers. In addition, the company generates wind power. It exports its products to Dubai, Saudi Arabia, and China. The company serves various industries, including textile, machine tool, utility, electric vehicle, process, renewable energy, petrochemical, agricultural, automobile, telecom, and healthcare. Lakshmi Electrical Control Systems Limited was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Coimbatore, India."}}